multiflexi-server (0.1.5) UNRELEASED; urgency=medium

  [ CyberVitexus ]
  * Fix apps.json/runtemplates.json returning an ID-keyed object instead
    of a JSON array (schema declared array, server emitted object).

  [ vitex ]
  * Fix RunTemplate.active returned as int instead of bool on single-
    record GET; success/fail returned '' instead of null when empty.
  * Fix AppApi::setAppById referencing an undefined $suffix variable
    (pre-existing bug, always fell through to HTML output regardless of
    requested format).
  * Remove dead StatusApi.php: extended a nonexistent AbstractStatusApi,
    never wired into any route; GET /status.json already works correctly
    via DefaultApi::statusSuffixGet.
  * Implement UserApi (was a stub, listUsers caused a 500), CompanyApi
    (was a 0-byte file, caused 501).
  * Relocate TaskApi.php from the wrong repo (multiflexi-api) into this
    one and wire it in; fix its list/get responses to match the schema's
    declared bare array/object shape (was wrapping under 'tasks'/'task'
    keys).
  * Implement EventruleApi, EventsourceApi (incl.
    testEventSourceConnection), CredentialApi, CredentialTypeApi,
    TopicApi, UserCompanyApi, UserRoleApi - all previously 501 due to
    missing concrete classes or missing OpenAPI tags.

 -- CyberVitexus <cybervitexus@gmail.com>  Wed, 15 Jul 2026 08:22:50 +0200

